description: The start of this work is quite astonishing and almost accidental. An image in very soft tones and looking for an effect the result appears completely unexpected. What I see is there and immediately makes me think of convolutions of a brain, but I cannot get rid of the starting image which has nothing to do with it anymore. You only see the result and I am the image of the start that remains present. Its second name could be "the views of the mind".
